                                    <li>Indian Military Academy (IMA) and Officers’ Training Academy (OTA) </li>
                                    <li>Indian Naval Academy (INA)</li>
                                    <li>Air Force Academy (AFA)</li>
                                </ul>
                                <p><b>Educational Qualification:</b></p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Graduation from a recognised university</li>
                                    <li>Engineering degree from a recognised university/institute </li>
                                    <li>Graduation (with Physics and Mathematics at Class 12) or Bachelor of Engineering</li>
                                </ul>
                                <p>Those who are in their final year of graduation can also apply. Women candidates are only eligible to apply for OTA. Candidates both male and female must meet the physical standard specified by UPSC.</p>
